item.title: Project-AudioBook
item.description:
ProjectAudioBook is non-profit organization, run by students who are very passionate to cater back to the society.

We believe that Anyone can achieve so many things by just learning from the books and novels. But many times big books and lengthy novels are very hectic and time-consuming to read. So we thought to do this Project-AudioBook.
